{
  "name": "04 — Wiki Ingestion Pipeline",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "manual-trigger",
      "name": "Manual Trigger",
      "position": [208, 304],
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "fileFolder",
        "returnAll": true,
        "filter": {
          "driveId": {
            "__rl": true,
            "mode": "list",
            "value": "My Drive"
          },
          "folderId": {
            "__rl": true,
            "mode": "id",
            "value": "FOLDER_ID_AQUI"
          }
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "list-files",
      "name": "List Wiki Files",
      "position": [432, 304],
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive",
      "typeVersion": 3
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "loop",
      "name": "Loop Over Items",
      "position": [640, 304],
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.splitInBatches",
      "typeVersion": 3
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "download",
        "fileId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "id",
          "value": "={{ $json.id }}"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "download",
      "name": "Download File",
      "position": [864, 304],
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive",
      "typeVersion": 3
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "insert",
        "tableName": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "list",
          "value": "documents"
        },
        "embeddingBatchSize": 50,
        "options": {
          "queryName": "match_documents"
        }
      },
      "id": "vector-store-insert",
      "name": "Supabase Vector Store",
      "position": [1088, 304],
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.vectorStoreSupabase",
      "typeVersion": 1.3
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "dataType": "binary",
        "options": {
          "metadata": {
            "metadataValues": [
              {
                "name": "source",
                "value": "={{ $('Download File').item.json.name }}"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "doc-loader",
      "name": "Document Loader",
      "position": [1088, 528],
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.documentDefaultDataLoader",
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "chunkOverlap": 200,
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "text-splitter",
      "name": "Text Splitter",
      "position": [1088, 704],
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.textSplitterRecursiveCharacterTextSplitter",
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "embeddings-insert",
      "name": "OpenAI Embeddings",
      "position": [1312, 528],
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.embeddingsOpenAi",
      "typeVersion": 1.2
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📥 Wiki Ingestion Pipeline\n\n**Flujo 04** — Pipeline de ingesta.\n\nLee archivos markdown de Google Drive,\nlos divide en chunks, genera embeddings\ncon OpenAI, y los almacena en Supabase pgvector.\n\n**Pasos:**\n1. Cambiar FOLDER_ID_AQUI por el ID real del folder en Drive\n2. Crear credencial Google Drive OAuth2\n3. Ejecutar manualmente",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 300,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "sticky-info",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "position": [160, 80],
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
